content.body: elijah-456: Welcome to our chat room. Please note that there are over 800 participants and we try to maintain a high "signal to noise" ratio, which is also why people usually don't greet or respond to greeting over the course of the day. If you want to participate in the WHATWG, I recommend you take a look at https://participate.whatwg.org/ and the various links from there
